bug.short_desc: Numberic list formatting issue in 2nd Edition PDF

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 79 screenshot of 2nd edition pdf
Section 9.2.10, there's an error in the numbering of the steps. It goes
1. 2. 3. 4. 5. a. b. 1. <-- whoops c. 6.
The 1 should be c and the c should be d.

Fixed in the HTML version of 2nd edition: www.ecma-international.org/ecma-402/2.0/
And confirmed in the draft for the 3rd Edition: https://tc39.github.io/ecma402/
